Feature: login

  The login feature takes the username and password and sets the user for the session

  Example: Sam, an admin user, wants to log in to create a new admin user. he enters his information and it lets him in
Feature: View task
    
    the view task feature list all task that are assinged to the user or assinged to all users.

    Example: Anna wants to view all her task she currently needs to work on. She opens the app and views them

Feature: Create task
    
    Allows user to add and assign task

    Example: Allen wants to assign sam a task titled "Add xyz feature". He enters the task information and creates it.

Feature: Delete task

    Allows basic users to delete task they create and admin users to delete any task

    Example: Anna accidently created a new task when one already existed so she uses the delete task feature